<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA33">
<l>yātāṉu moṉṟaṟiyiṟ ṟaṉṉukakki leṉkolō</l>
<l>yātāṉu nērntaṇukā vāṟutāṉ yātāṉun</l>
<l>tēṟumā ceyyā vacurarkaḷai nēmiyāṟ</l>
<l>pāṟupā ṟākkiṉāṉ pāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one knows anything, if one rejoices in him, what</l>
<l>is the way not to get close, accepting everything,</l>
<l>to him who has brought into just ruin,</l>
<l>with [his] discus], the Asuras who clearly did not do anything?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
